quran[12{c,v,t}:
20,114,to khuda jo sacha badshah hai aliiiii qader hai. aur quran ki wahi jo tumhari taraf bhaije jati hai is ke poora honay se pehlay quran ke ( parhnay ke ) liye jaldi nahkiya karo aur dua karo ke mere perwar-digaar mujhe aur ziyada ilm day
20,115,aur hum ne pehlay aadam se ehad liya tha magar woh ( usay ) bhool gay aur hum ne un mein sabr وثبات nah dekha
20,116,aur jab hum ne firshton se kaha ke aadam ke agay sajda karo to sab sjday mein gir parre magar iblees ne inkaarkiya
20,117,hum ne farmaya ke aadam yeh tumhara aur tumhari biwi ka dushman hai to yeh kahin tum dono ko bahisht se nikalwa nah day. phir tum takleef meinparr jao
20,118,yahan tum ko yeh ( asayish ) hogi ke nah bhukay raho nah nangay
20,119,aur yeh ke nah pyase raho aur nah dhoop khao
20,120,to shetan ne un ke dil mein waswasa dala. ( aur ) kaha ke aadam bhala mein tum ko ( aisa ) darakht batau ( jo ) hamesha ki zindagi ka ( Samrah day ) aur ( aisi ) badshahat ke kabhi zael nah ho
20,121,to dono ne is darakht ka phal kha liya to un par un ki sharmgahain zahir hogyin aur woh apne ( badnon ) par bahisht ke pattey chipkanay lagey. aur aadam ne apne perwar-digaar ke hukum ke khilaaf kiya to ( woh apne matloob se ) bay-raah ho gay-ay
20,122,phir un ke perwar-digaar ne un ko nawaza to un par meharbani se tavajja farmai aur seedhi raah batayi
20,123,farmaya ke tum dono yahan se neechay utar jao. tum mein baaz baaz ke dushman ( hon ge ) phir agar meri taraf se tumahray paas hadaayat aeye to jo shakhs meri hadaayat ki pairwi kere ga woh nah gumraah hoga aur nah takleef mein parre ga
20,124,aur jo meri nasiyaat se munh phairay ga is ki zindagi tang hojaye gi aur qayamat ko hum usay andha karkay utthayen ge
20,125,woh kahe ga mere perwar-digaar to ne mujhe andha karkay kyun uthaya mein to daikhta bhalta tha
